'''華川郡'''（{{kor|諺=화천군|漢=華川郡|羅=Hwacheon gun|f=y}}）位於[[大韓民國|大韓民國]][[江原道_(南)|江原道]]北部，北边和[[朝韩非军事区|朝韩非军事区]]接壤。

华川郡每年1-2月举行的[[华川山鳟鱼庆典|华川山鳟鱼庆典]]曾被美国[[CNN|CNN]]以“冬季七大奇迹”介绍<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.chinatimes.com/cn/realtimenews/20141227002451-260405 | title =韩国冬季庆典开跑，冰上活动玩不完 | publisher =中时电子报 | date =2014-12-27 | access-date =2018-01-20 | archive-date =2018-01-19 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180119120135/http://www.chinatimes.com/cn/realtimenews/20141227002451-260405 | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url =http://chinese.yonhapnews.co.kr/newpgm/9908000000.html?cid=ACK20171212004000881 | title =2018华川山鳟鱼庆典1月6日开幕 | publisher =韩联社 | date =2017-12-14 | access-date =2018-01-20 | archive-date =2018-01-20 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180120124433/http://chinese.yonhapnews.co.kr/newpgm/9908000000.html?cid=ACK20171212004000881 | dead-url =no }}</ref>，是与中国哈尔滨冰雪节、日本札幌冰雪节、加拿大魁北克冬季狂欢节并列世界四大冰雪节的韩国达标性冬季庆典<ref>{{cite web | url =http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2017-01/9941596.html | title =韩华川山鳟鱼庆典将举行 并列世界四大冬季庆典 | publisher =环球网 | date =2017-01-13 | access-date =2018-01-20 | archive-date =2018-01-20 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180120182205/http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2017-01/9941596.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

